    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: 'You are training to recover signal relics.


    Each round, you will
    be told what kind of relic to find.

    Use Previous / Next to move focus between
    stations.

    Press Select to choose the focused station.


    Controls:

    Arrow
    Keys / 1 & 2 / Gamepad D-Pad = Change focus

    Space / Enter / E / Gamepad
    South = Select

    Mouse / Touch = Click a station directly


    Accessibility
    Mode adds longer announcements and larger text.'
